<div class="container" id="about">
    <span class="title">About me</span>
    <div class="content">
        <p>I'm web-developer from Russia.</p>
        <p>I know...
            <ul>
                <li>PHP</li>
                <li>Ruby</li>
                <li>Python</li>
                <li><i class="fa fa-language"></i> Russian</li>
                <li><i class="fa fa-language"></i> English</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <p>I use...
            <ul>
                <li>Middleman and Sinatra</li>
                <li>GitHub Pages</li>
                <li><a href="//komodoide.com">Komodo IDE</a></li>
                <li><a href="/materia">Materia</a> scheme in Terminal and the editor</li>
